# Hero

`Hero` is a large, page-header-like element that draws big attention from the user, with large text
to promote a headline for the rest of the page.

{% showcase %}

```
<Hero>
  <Header tag="h1" variant="header-xl/normal">Hello</Header>
  <Text variant="text-lg/normal">This is a sample Hero element.</Text>
</Hero>
```

{% /showcase %}
